  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hobo Cat Adventures</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/243f951d8e921a00fba30d521e7816a5.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/243f951d8e921a00fba30d521e7816a5.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/243f951d8e921a00fba30d521e7816a5.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Hobo Cat Adventures you play as a homeless cat willing to do every job there is on offer. You travel to the Squirrel Kingdom – a place full of weird characters, dangerous enemies and lots of treasures to find. King Daniel, party animal and ruler of the Squirrel Kingdom, has got a special job for you! Ring the three bells of awakening!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D Platformer</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/01a285c7185b9a8e3ac4b19c05d26d84.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/01a285c7185b9a8e3ac4b19c05d26d84.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/01a285c7185b9a8e3ac4b19c05d26d84.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Jump your way through the Squirrel Kingdom to collect all sorts of valuable treasures! In the Squirrel Kingdom it’s all about the money! You need to find enough moneybags to proceed to different areas of the Squirrel Kingdom. Collect coins to unlock new weapons or buy a homeless cat some coffee!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/dbed3a31dfc59038b5850dc6073f2c34.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/dbed3a31dfc59038b5850dc6073f2c34.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/dbed3a31dfc59038b5850dc6073f2c34.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight against an assortment of dangerous enemies, all with unique attack patterns. Attack your foes with a handful of different, unique weapons like a dead fish or a 5-string banjo. Avoid incoming attacks by dodging or parrying them.  Lock on to your enemies in this Souls inspired combat system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/d59084ef7b65e5a2321851086628aa34.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/d59084ef7b65e5a2321851086628aa34.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/d59084ef7b65e5a2321851086628aa34.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Parry your enemies by hitting them at the right moment with a thrown item. Once parried, perform a devastating deathblow attack that recovers some of your health.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Items</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/094a28152dab31e404aace7b8353c18e.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/094a28152dab31e404aace7b8353c18e.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/094a28152dab31e404aace7b8353c18e.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Pick up, throw and use tons of different items. Throw bombs, ride on chicken, drink coffee or get drunk consuming “Hobo Brew”. Are you ready to pee-hover while playing the banjo?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jobs</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/3453aa4b291afc4a46d05b11a9acd38f.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/3453aa4b291afc4a46d05b11a9acd38f.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/3453aa4b291afc4a46d05b11a9acd38f.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are a lot of ways to make a buck in the Squirrel Kingdom. Meet weird characters, all with even weirder jobs for you to complete. Earn cash for easy tasks or even get a bag full of gold for more difficult jobs. Use this cash to buy new weapons, open new areas or buy a homeless cat some coffee!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Facts</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Visit 7 areas<br></li><li>Collect 24 gold bags<br></li><li>Defeat 6 Bosses<br></li><li>Find 7 unique weapons<br></li><li>Ring 3 bells<br></li><li>Unlock 42 achievements<br></li><li>Two different endings<br></li><li>Souls inspired lock-on combat system<br></li><li>Cartoony blood and gore<br></li><li>Meet weird, unique characters<br></li><li>Contains a lot of (im)mature humour<br></li><li>Lovingly made by only one person</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Photosensitivity Warning</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/57fec9b102cf6dccb7ad95b68c61740a.poster.avif?t=1773177277\" width=576 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/57fec9b102cf6dccb7ad95b68c61740a.webm?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438090/extras/57fec9b102cf6dccb7ad95b68c61740a.mp4?t=1773177277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is a section in the game which contains rapidly flashing lights and color changes (see image above). Please consult your physician before playing.<br><br>Add Hobo Cat Adventures to your wish list now to help a homeless cat!",
